item.title: Writeup for TexsawCTF 2024
item.description: Overview Although the challenges of the tournament look simple, they are actually quite difficult and my way of doing things is also very stupid lol. Some challenges I even did manually. It takes several hours for them. Really had a sleepless night. Anyway, thanks for reading and have a great day! Note : Data file in my blogs/static/Texsaw2024 dir Solution 1.
